skills.lock

# Scratch / temp files
tmp_*
*.tmp
.tmp-*
.pending-*.sh
.run-*.sh
.notify-feature-*.sh
.notify-feature-*.txt
.*-tmp.md
.*-draft.md
.*-msg.txt
*_msg.txt
*_raw.txt

# Feature-skill scratch verifiers — repo-root only (past leak shapes
